====================
Base Onchange Rules
====================

Allow to store fields settings (default values, allowed values, etc)
to drive a specific behavior on any model/record

Usage
=====


.. image:: https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas
    :alt: Try me on Runbot
    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/149/10.0


Known issues / Roadmap
======================

- To make UI more readable (for certain users) allow to hide fields with according a new group.


